## Quick Start

```bash
# Authenticate
darkfield auth login

# Run a demo
darkfield analyze demo --trait sycophancy

# Check your usage
darkfield billing usage
```

## Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -e .

# Run tests
pytest

# Build distribution
python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel
```

## Publishing

```bash
# PyPI
python -m twine upload dist/*

# NPM (wrapper)
npm publish
```
